<span class="line"><span>0 * * * * /usr/local/bin/php /home/odah/www/eat-posla/api/cron/reservation-cleanup.php &gt;&gt; /home/odah/log/cron-reservation-cleanup.log 2&gt;&amp;1</span></span>
